00:00:24.056 --> 00:00:29.085
 When I rise to preach the gospel, I often preach to people, 

00:00:29.437 --> 00:00:34.476
 who do not know God because they worship idols. 

00:00:34.921 --> 00:00:38.132
 Really terrible idols. 

00:00:43.397 --> 00:00:48.412
 They cover their table with their gods. 

00:00:49.356 --> 00:00:55.438
 I tell them that the Christian God works the opposite. 

00:00:57.220 --> 00:01:02.233
 She covers the table for her children. 

00:01:05.592 --> 00:01:11.087
 In other religions, people are always looking for God. 

00:01:12.674 --> 00:01:17.691
 In Christianity, God is looking for man. 

